OK. Here it is. Made in 1 day, less. 
I kinda was inspired by some skins I saw, so I made up a pack of "Desert" themed skins. 
And so the idea of this map was born. 
It combinds Valves De_Dust2 & De_Dust. 
Note; I did not de-compile the maps.

Beta;
http://www.fpsbanana.com/maps/148841

Anyway...
This maps features;
Lots of Decals.
Two Towers.
Many many props from Dust2 & Dust.
Ai Noded. (Un intentionally.)
Multiple spawns. 30+
Custom made SkyBox.
Multiple features from Dust2 & Dust.
+ Lots more, as seen in images. 

Server using map;
69.197.191.101:27015

OKAY. 

There are custom textures, I don't have the tools required to include them in the bsp. So.. I simply gave you the materials inside the "Materials"  folder.
